{
  "stem": "25423.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he wasn't beatified.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a lengthy process.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's still ongoing, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The formal, first phase of the process is finished.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I helped with Postulation, as it is called, and collecting documents and doing research.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they quickly became aware that I can testify not only to the activities connected with saving and sheltering Jews, but I am also able to assist in unraveling the complex political and economical social situation in this part of the world during the lifetime of this individual.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Part of my life, because they see the picture of the Metropolitan and his brother is in my bedroom.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These are people, my benefactors, thanks to whom I live.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Father Marek, as long as he was alive, used to come and visit me and visit my children.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Many other monks came and went.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The older boys are named Andrew and Clement to commemorate the fact that these two extraordinary human beings saved not only my life, but befriended Jews at a time when nobody was interested to befriend Jews, and had compassion.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Very rare phenomenon in this part of the world at that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGH]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I have made clear that I am brought up as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I am a Jew and I think like a Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Whether this is a particular advantage, my answer is no.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why and how, it's a long discussion, not related here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I always could dissolve in the Christian world at choice, because among Ukrainians, to this day, I'm not recognized as a non-Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The same applies to the Poles.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
